ss:Type="String">{DamageDebuff} is a percentage.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENERGY_DRAIN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{EnergyDrainChance}[strengthentropy/] strength chance to apply [abilityred]Energy Drain[/abilityred] to targets for {duration}[turn/]. On success, the caster gains an [abilityblue]Essence Charge[/abilityblue].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Szansa (siła {EnergyDrainChance}[strengthentropy/]) na spowodowanie [abilityred]wyssania energii[/abilityred] na {duration}[turn/]. W razie sukcesu napastnik zyskuje [abilityblue]ładunek esencji[/abilityblue].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPIC_DECAY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Entropic Decay</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rozkład entropiczny</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="8" ss:StyleID="s64"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPIC_DECAY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The unit is taking {DecayDamage}[damageEntropy/] per [turn/] and has -{EntropyWeakness}[DefenseEntropy/].[br/]This effect can stack up to {StackAmount} times.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostka odnosi {DecayDamage}[damageEntropy/] pkt. obrażeń na [turn/] i ma –{EntropyWeakness}[DefenseEntropy/].[br/]Efekt może się sumować do {StackAmount} razy.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="8" ss:StyleID="s64"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPIC_DECAY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{EntropicDecayChance}[strengthEntropy/] strength chance to apply [abilityred]Entropic Decay[/abilityred] to units for {durationEntropicDecay}[turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Szansa (siła {EntropicDecayChance}[strengthEntropy/]) na spowodowanie [abilityred]rozkładu entropicznego[/abilityred] u jednostek na {durationEntropicDecay}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="8" ss:StyleID="s64"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MUTANT_GOOP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Mutant Goop</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zmutowane paskudztwo</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MUTANT_GOOP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Mutant or Xenoplague units entering or ending their turn on this hex gain [abilityblue]Blood Fury[/abilityblue] for {DurationPositive}[turn/].[br/]Biological and Cyborg units, that aren't Mutants or Xenoplague, have an {MutantGoop} chance to inflict [abilityred]Poisoned[/abilityred] for {DurationNegative}[turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostki mutantów lub Ksenozarazy, wchodzące na to pole lub kończące na nim turę, zyskują [abilityblue]krwawą furię[/abilityblue] na {DurationPositive}[turn/].[br/]Jednostki organiczne i cyborgi nienależące do mutantów ani Ksenozarazy mają szansę {MutantGoop} na doznanie [abilityred]zatrucia[/abilityred] na {DurationNegative}[turn/]</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ESSENCE_POOL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Essence Pool</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sadzawka esencji</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ESSENCE_POOL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Units ending their turn in an Essence Pool gain an [abilityblue]Essence Charge[/abilityblue].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostki kończące turę w sadzawce esencji zyskują [abilityblue]ładunek esencji[/abilityblue].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLEAK_ESSENCE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROP_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bleak Essence</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ponura Esencja</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLEAK_ESSENCE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROP_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">When this unit dies, it transforms into a Desolate under permanent control of the one who inflicted this status.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gdy ta jednostka polegnie, zmieni się w opuszczonego pod kontrolą tego gracza, który wywołał u niej ten stan.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Desolate as in the Forgotten Unit</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ROT_POOL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rot Essence Pool</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sadzawka zgniłej Esencji</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ROT_POOL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Non-Forgotten units ending their turn in a Rot Essence Pool have an {strchance}[strengthentropy/] chance suffer [abilityred]Essence Drain[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostki nienależące do Zapomnianych, które kończą turę w sadzawce zgniłej Esencji, mają szansę o sile {strchance}[strengthentropy/] na doznanie [abilityred]wyssania esencji[/abilityred].</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="